rows.label: campfev11_670_175_msg0001
rows.name:
Sata, it's almost time
for the final battle.

rows.label: campfev11_670_175_msg0005
rows.name:
We need to make sure
we don't hold anyone back.

rows.label: campfev11_670_175_msg0008
rows.name: Hey, hey. We're not going yet.

rows.label: campfev11_670_175_msg0009
rows.name:
First, we're heading back to
the inn in the capital
to get some rest.

rows.label: campfev11_670_175_msg0012
rows.name:
We need to be in peak
condition to beat Metsu.

rows.label: campfev11_670_175_msg0013
rows.name:
If you lose focus for even a second,
it could be fatal.

rows.label: campfev11_670_175_msg0014
rows.name:
That's why we're going to rest
at the inn in the capital.

rows.label: campfev11_670_175_msg0016
rows.name: You get some good rest too, Sata.
